              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14956981/" class="">第25页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46146557/" class=" " title="酗酒少女KOI酱">酗酒少女KOI酱</a>
                (Let us be alone together)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14956981">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">真理不仅在【人生而平等】，也在每个民族都有同等的智慧  ~~ </span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-10-19 22:13</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                真理不仅在【人生而平等】，也在每个民族都有同等的智慧  ~~ 
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
